author: dlr
msg: JavaHL: Fix SVNAdmin's setRevProp() and setLog() APIs, which have been
broken since the setLog() implementation first appeared in r8652,
apparently improperly copied from the options parsing code in
subversion/svnadmin/main.c.
* subversion/bindings/java/javahl/native/SVNAdmin.cpp
(SVNAdmin::setRevProp): Remove checking of the svn_opt_revision_kind
field of the REVISION parameter, which was originally intended to
check the end revision in the options to the command-line
'svnadmin' client.
